rComments: Professor Papazoglou is an amazing Professor. I took PSY333 with him, and you really just need to memorize the Lecture Slides for an 80 - 90 %, and if you want 90 - 100 % read the easy textbook. Straightforward tests, and easy marker. I would recommend as many classes with him as possible. He teaches really well and wants his students to do well.

Nice Professor, he responded to all my email on time. Read textbook, it will be important for MC. The Short/Long answer questions are based on lecture placed in real life scenarios ( which not as difficult as you might imagine, attend lecture and you will do amazing). He provides  good examples to understand difficult concepts. Very friendly.

The professor is great, he is understandable and explains the material well. The professor provides an easy and  friendly environment. I would take another class with this professor as he is easy and understandable. I would recommend this class to anyone that needs an easy, and small course load class.
Very good prof! Had interesting lectures with many real world examples. Easygoing and polite.

The professor is very clear, productive, interactive in his lectures. He provides extra material with videos that are very helpful and invites very inspiring guest lecturers.  He is very kind, understanding and offers a very positive learning experience, which compared to other courses is mostly stress free. The term examinations are trick-free.

The best course I have taken so far in 3 years of school. The prof is amazing! always there to answer questions and makes the effort to know the students. He is one of the professors and I would definitely like to take any course he teaches :)
